[32m+[m[32m- Strong typing improves reliability.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Request models define system boundaries.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Response models improve consistency.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Public contracts should evolve carefully.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Pydantic provides robust validation.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Contracts should be stable across releases.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Breaking changes require careful planning.[m
