[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Exception Handling[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Errors should be standardized.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Global exception handlers improve consistency.[m
[32m+[m[32m- HTTP status codes communicate intent.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Internal exceptions should not leak implementation details.[m
