[32m+[m[32m- Consistent error formats simplify client handling.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Logging should capture error context.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## API Testing[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Test endpoints independently.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Validate request models.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Validate response models.[m
