[32m+[m[32m## 8. Lessons Learned[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### API Design[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- REST APIs are interface layers rather than business layers.[m
[32m+[m[32m- API routes should remain thin and delegate work to the Application Layer.[m
