[32m+[m[32m- OpenAPI documentation significantly improves discoverability and developer experience.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Engineering Practice[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Dependency Injection simplifies application lifecycle management in service-oriented architectures.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Pydantic provides reliable request validation and response serialization.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Global exception handling ensures consistent error responses.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Automated integration testing provides confidence in API functionality.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Architecture[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Enterprise APIs depend on stable contracts rather than implementation details.[m
[32m+[m[32m- The separation between API Layer and Application Layer preserves modular architecture.[m
[32m+[m[32m- FastAPI enables rapid development without compromising enterprise standards.[m
